        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>Large orders</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'> generated the highest sales by a significant margin, followed by medium and small orders. This suggests that higher-quantity orders are a major driver of Q1 revenue, so Q2 promotions could encourage customers to buy in bundles or larger quantities.</run>
